text: "She's Not There" is a 1964 debut single by English band The Zombies and is the leading single from their debut studio album Begin Here. It went to number 2 in the United States and Canada, number 1 in New Zealand and Japan and number 12 in the United Kingdom. == Santana cover == In 1977, She's Not There was covered by Santana for their debut studio album Moonflower. It went to number 11 in the United Kingdom, number 27 in the United States, number 19 in Australia, number 21 in Canada, number 9 in New Zealand, number 4 in Ireland and number 3 in the Netherlands. ==References== Category:1964 songs Category:Debut singles Category:The Zombies songs Category:Santana (band) songs Category:Jazz rock songs Category:Pop rock songs Category:Baroque pop songs Category:Latin rock songs
